    Description

    The Apple Store app is the most personalized and seamless way to browse, learn about, and shop the latest Apple products, no matter where you are.


    DISCOVER WHAT’S NEW IN THE PRODUCTS TAB

    Explore product recommendations that are tailored to you, and even shop for accessories that are compatible with products you already own.

    Browse the latest iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple Watch, and more. Discover the latest seasonal offerings, and exclusive ways to save — available only at Apple.

    Get shopping support from a Specialist via phone, over text, or locate your nearest store and visit us in-person.


    FIND YOUR MOST RELEVANT INFORMATION IN THE FOR YOU TAB

    Save and organize your favorites, and easily continue shopping where you left off with Recent Activity.

    Conveniently track your order status every step of the way, and be ready when it arrives.

    Get personalized notifications and be the first to know about new announcements and offers.


    MAKE THE MOST OF THE DEVICES YOU ALREADY OWN IN THE GO FURTHER TAB

    Get creative tips from our team with videos, sessions, and more.

    Sign up and reserve your spot in a Today at Apple session at your local Apple Store.

    Easily connect with us to find the right support options for any technical or account issues.


    A BETTER WAY TO SHOP

    Manage your account information including stored payments, shipping address, AppleCare status, as well as your Account Balance.

    Add a personal touch with free custom engraving. And even use your Memoji — an Apple Store app exclusive feature.

    Get answers to common questions with Specialist-led videos that can help walk you through your options during your purchase.

    Utilize AR to see how our products will look in your space.

    When you visit an Apple Store, quickly scan and pay for accessories with Self-Checkout, or hop into in an upcoming Today at Apple session.


    - 

    The app may ask permission to use the TrueDepth camera to help with Apple Vision Pro fit.

    Note that the Apple Store app and certain features are available only in select countries.

    How your data is used:
    To create a personalized shopping experience, we’ll collect and use data about your device, Apple account, Apple Store shopping activity, and Apple subscriptions. To change or modify any of these settings, go to Account > Settings

    Ratings and Reviews

    126.5K Ratings

    126.5K Ratings

    jmaeser , 11/16/2024

    No Dark Mode Icon?

    I use this app often to browse and purchase Apple products. It works great. As of recent iPadOS 18 which introduced a better dark mode experience with specific dark mode icons, this app has yet to update from the stark white background when placed into dark mode. For an Apple specific app, you’d think this would have changed by now? Nearly 99% of the other apps have, and this is updated on iPhone. It sounds like a small annoyance, but when looking at a home screen, or app drawer and there is a singular eye sore and from the developers of the OS itself… it’s a bummer.

    Doniaaa18 , 09/25/2024

    Extremely Disappointed with Customer Service and Repair Costs

    I recently purchased a MacBook Air M3 in July 2024, and my experience with the company has been nothing short of frustrating. After a rain incident, some water got into my laptop, and I rushed to the store for help.

    Upon arrival, I was initially told that I needed an appointment, but thankfully, a kind staff member allowed me to see someone after noticing my distress. However, the technician took a long time to arrive and, when he finally did, his attitude was dismissive. He even joked about the model being an Air, not a Pro, before shocking me with a repair quote of 1,100!

    I wasn't the only one facing issues—there were others in the store with similar problems, which raises concerns about the quality of these products. The lack of genuine customer service and the outrageous repair costs have left me feeling extremely let down. I expected better from a brand with such a strong reputation.

    I hope the company improves its customer service and addresses these issues, as I certainly won't be returning anytime soon. I will switch all my devices to better companies my parents have samsung and we never have been through all this mess before i will not wait i will but my iphone and ipad as a trade in better company

    OKBoomer00 , 11/14/2024

    Needs more work; needs Vision Pro app

    It would be inspiring to me and likely the developers to witness Apple pushing the boundaries of its technologies. This app serves as just one example where I envisioned Apple leading the way in digital shopping. However, the absence of a Vision Pro app is particularly disappointing. Moreover, the current state of the app limits customers’ ability to zoom in on marketing photos. While the pop-up boxes offer an immersive glimpse into display technology on the iPad, they are confined to a small box on a large screen. It would be commendable if Apple paid more attention to the finer details, design, and long-term usability of devices in the app.

    Lastly, I kindly request an update on when the order tracking feature in Apple’s Wallet app will be synced with Apple Store app purchases.

    Thank you for your attention to this matter.
